**[Orc 6 Flees — Life Too Short]**
- Orc 6 (receptive), watching all his companions run, decides to flee as well.

**[GM]** — *narrating Orc 6's decision*
> "You know, he's seeing all of his buddies run, He's like, you know… He's like, there's this bright light, he's kind of going to himself."

**[David Mendenhall / Vukradin]** — *calling after him*
> "It's okay, you can go. Just tell your friends about Lathander."

**[GM]**
> "And it's like… You know, he's kind of decided that life's too short. He's running."

**[David Mendenhall / Vukradin]**
> "Another flea, alright."

